setDestProjection

void setDestProjection(java.lang.String toEPSG)
Set this variable to tell the driver in which projection do you want your data. If the driver can reproject to this new EPSG, it will return true in canReproject. NOTE: use String strEPSG = mapCtrl.getViewPort() .getProjection().getAbrev() .substring(5); Otherwise, it will return false.

Parameters:
toEPSG -

canReproject

boolean canReproject(java.lang.String toEPSGdestinyProjection)
Returns:
true if the driver will be able to deliver the entities in the destiny projection. False otherwise.
